"1 stick unsalted butter, softened","3/4 cup sugar","2  large eggs","1  vanilla bean, seeds scraped","1 tablespoon dark rum","2 1/2 cups all-purpose flour","1/2 cup unsweetened cocoa powder","1 teaspoon baking powder","3/4 teaspoon salt","1/2 teaspoon cinnamon","1 1/2 cups raw pistachios, plus chopped pistachios for garnish","1  large egg white, lightly beaten","  Melted bittersweet chocolate, for dipping"